<img class="alignnone wp-image-17477 size-full" src="http://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12-BridgtonProewe1.jpg" alt="12 BridgtonProewe1" width="800" height="533" srcset="http://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12-BridgtonProewe1.jpg 800w, http://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12-BridgtonProewe1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12-BridgtonProewe1-768x512.jpg 768w, http://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12-BridgtonProewe1-672x448.jpg 672w, http://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12-BridgtonProewe1-405x270.jpg 405w, http://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/12-BridgtonProewe1-480x320.jpg 480w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /> Die Bridgton Rugbyklub het Saterdag op die velde van die Oudtshoorn Vaardigheidskool proewe gehou om sy spanne vir die komende seisoen te help saamstel. Links bo hardloop Charlton Ewerts met die bal en regs bo Hardus Coetzee. Die klub het tans meer as 120 spe­lers en speel sy eerste wedstryd Saterdag, 10 Februarie, teen Progress op George. Foto’s: Ebenezer Titus 